{
  "texts": [
    "Consequently, a compelling need exists for automated Hyper-parameter optimization to alleviate computational demands and minimize user intervention.",
    "Utilizing the steepest gradient descent algorithm for optimizing Hyper-parameter configurations proves unsuitable [72].",
    "Instead, prominent techniques such as Grid Search and Random Search have emerged to address this challenge effectively.",
    "Grid search is a brute-force approach to Hyper-parameter tuning.",
    "It evaluates all possible combinations of Hyper-parameter values [73], whereas Random Search adopts a more stochastic approach by exploring random subsets of Hyper-parameter combinations [74]."
  ]
}